255
00:13:06,692 --> 00:13:08,442
[AKI]
It'll just be the two of us!

256
00:13:08,525 --> 00:13:10,192
[AKI sighs]

257
00:13:10,275 --> 00:13:12,692
[YUZU] Bask in that
joy while you can, kid.

258
00:13:12,775 --> 00:13:14,358
