284
00:14:21,858 --> 00:14:23,358
[BOTH giggle]

285
00:14:23,442 --> 00:14:25,858
[AKI] Here Teacher, you can
sit on this cushion.

286
00:14:25,942 --> 00:14:27,942
[AYAKA]
