305
00:15:26,817 --> 00:15:28,650
[AKI gasps]

306
00:15:28,733 --> 00:15:30,400
Is something wrong?

307
00:15:36,567 --> 00:15:39,150
[AKI]
I can... I can do this!

308
00:15:39,233 --> 00:15:40,317
[AYAKA]
Hm.

309
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,483
Uh?

310
00:15:47,775 --> 00:15:50,775
[AKI whimpers]

311
00:15:50,858 --> 00:15:52,275
[AYAKA]
Hm...

312
00:15:53,817 --> 00:15:55,067
[AKI grunts]

313
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:57,733
Oh. I think you put your
answers in the wrong spot.

314
00:15:57,817 --> 00:16:00,233
