315
00:16:00,317 --> 00:16:01,817
Right over here.

316
00:16:01,900 --> 00:16:05,400
[AKI] Oh, you're right.
Thanks for catching that.

317
00:16:08,192 --> 00:16:11,067
[AKI grunts]
I can't concentrate!

318
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:14,108
Do you think we could maybe take
a break for a minute or two?

319
00:16:14,192 --> 00:16:16,525
[AYAKA] It doesn't look like
you're done yet, though.

320
00:16:16,608 --> 00:16:19,567
At this rate, you won't finish
by the end of the day.

321
00:16:19,650 --> 00:16:21,025
You can rest later.

322
00:16:21,108 --> 00:16:22,858
[AKI]
Can I go to the bathroom?

323
00:16:22,942 --> 00:16:25,525
[AYAKA] I think you can
wait a little longer.

324
00:16:25,608 --> 00:16:27,108
[AKI] I'm not trying to
squeeze a break in,

325
00:16:27,192 --> 00:16:28,942
I really have to go.

326
00:16:29,025 --> 00:16:30,358
[sighs]

327
00:16:36,733 --> 00:16:37,567
[AKI]
Hm?

328
00:16:37,650 --> 00:16:39,400
Hey!

329
00:16:39,483 --> 00:16:41,233
[AKI] And to think I was
so excited to do my

330
00:16:41,317 --> 00:16:42,442
homework with her.

331
00:16:42,525 --> 00:16:46,400
Who knew she'd be such
a strict taskmaster?

332
00:16:46,483 --> 00:16:48,400
[AYAKA]
You can do it, Akkun!

333
00:16:50,942 --> 00:16:53,108
Oh! I'm finally done.

334
00:16:53,192 --> 00:16:57,442
Fantastic job. You worked as
hard as you could the whole day.

335
00:16:57,525 --> 00:16:58,900
Such a good boy.

336
00:16:58,983 --> 00:17:02,233
[AKI sighs]

337
00:17:02,317 --> 00:17:03,525
[AKI]
Wait, I still have to pee!

338
00:17:03,608 --> 00:17:04,858
[door clatters]

339
00:17:04,942 --> 00:17:07,775
[toilet flushes]

340
00:17:11,275 --> 00:17:12,733
[AKI]
So, Teach?

341
00:17:12,817 --> 00:17:14,275
[AYAKA]
Hm?

342
00:17:14,358 --> 00:17:16,692
[AKI] We're done now, right?
Since I finished my homework?

343
00:17:16,775 --> 00:17:19,483
[AYAKA giggles]
Yes, you are.

344
00:17:19,567 --> 00:17:21,150
[AKI sighs]

345
00:17:21,233 --> 00:17:23,567
Just wait here
for a few moments.

346
00:17:25,108 --> 00:17:28,067
[AKI]
Ah! At last, my reward!

347
00:17:29,275 --> 00:17:30,942
Okay!

348
00:17:31,025 --> 00:17:31,900
[AKI gasps]

349
00:17:31,983 --> 00:17:33,817
Here yah go. Pick one!

350
00:17:36,983 --> 00:17:40,483
[AKI] It's not quite what I was
hoping for, but I'll take it.

351
00:17:40,567 --> 00:17:43,150
[AYAKA] I'll have the other
as a treat to myself.

352
00:17:45,567 --> 00:17:46,733
[AKI gasps]

353
00:17:49,483 --> 00:17:51,233
[AKI gasps]

354
00:17:51,317 --> 00:17:54,692
[AKI]
This is the real reward.

355
00:17:54,775 --> 00:17:55,442
[doorbell]

356
00:17:55,525 --> 00:17:57,108
[BOTH]
Uh?

357
00:17:57,192 --> 00:17:58,150
[NISHIKI]
Evening!

358
00:17:58,233 --> 00:18:00,317
Good evening Yatsuho!

359
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:02,150
[NISHIKI]
Why are you dressed like that?

360
00:18:02,233 --> 00:18:05,150
Because I'm playing the
part of a teacher today.

361
00:18:05,233 --> 00:18:08,067
[NISHIKI] Well, whatever.
Here's that juice you ordered!

362
00:18:08,150 --> 00:18:09,942
[AYAKA gigles]
Thanks for bringing it here

363
00:18:10,025 --> 00:18:11,358
on such a hot day.

364
00:18:11,442 --> 00:18:12,733
This is all juice?

365
00:18:12,817 --> 00:18:14,900
Yep, and you should
consider yourself lucky,

366
00:18:14,983 --> 00:18:16,983
because I import
the stuff specially.

367
00:18:17,067 --> 00:18:18,192
Really?

368
00:18:18,275 --> 00:18:20,108
Once everyone's finished
with their homework,

369
00:18:20,192 --> 00:18:22,150
I was planning to
have a little party.

370
00:18:22,233 --> 00:18:23,650
[AKI]
Whoa, awesome!

371
00:18:23,733 --> 00:18:26,233
[AYAKA] You came just as
we got Akkun's done.

372
00:18:26,317 --> 00:18:28,358
Oh yeah? Atta boy!

373
00:18:28,442 --> 00:18:30,400
[AKI grunts]

374
00:18:30,483 --> 00:18:34,233
And, by the way,
I threw this in as a gift.

375
00:18:34,317 --> 00:18:36,317
[AYAKA]
Oh! Thank you so much!

376
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:37,483
[AKI]
Hm?

377
00:18:39,233 --> 00:18:41,775
My little sister absolutely
loves this juice.

378
00:18:41,858 --> 00:18:44,525
If you don't mind me asking,
what's your little sister like?

379
00:18:44,608 --> 00:18:46,567
How can I describe her?

380
00:18:46,650 --> 00:18:49,275
Well, she's currently
a high schooler.

381
00:18:49,358 --> 00:18:52,692
She's very kind,
loves her grandma.

382
00:18:52,775 --> 00:18:54,317
[AKI]
She's related to Miss Caretaker,

383
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,692
so I imagine she's
gotta be great.

384
00:18:56,775 --> 00:18:57,983
[AYAKA]
She's a good fighter.

385
00:18:58,067 --> 00:18:59,525
Fighter?

386
00:18:59,608 --> 00:19:01,983
[AYAKA giggles] Shall we open
one of these juices up now?

387
00:19:02,067 --> 00:19:04,733
After all, we both know
you worked hard today!

388
00:19:04,817 --> 00:19:06,692
Just keep it between
the two of us.

389
00:19:06,775 --> 00:19:10,192
[AKI] Are you sure? I am
pretty curious how it tastes!

390
00:19:11,817 --> 00:19:14,567
[AKI gasps]

391
00:19:14,650 --> 00:19:16,608
Oh! I didn't read
the label until now,

392
00:19:16,692 --> 00:19:18,317
but Yatsuho gave me alcohol.

393
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,733
Sorry I opened it!

394
00:19:19,817 --> 00:19:22,358
Don't worry about it,
I'll just drink this instead.

395
00:19:22,442 --> 00:19:24,817
You wanted to try the juice,
so go ahead and have some.

396
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:26,442
Okay.

397
00:19:26,525 --> 00:19:29,275
[AYAKA] Now then.
To a fun summer break!

398
00:19:29,358 --> 00:19:30,108
[AKI]
Yeah!

399
00:19:30,192 --> 00:19:31,483
[BOTH]
Cheers!

400
00:19:36,650 --> 00:19:38,275
[AKI]
I feel so adult.

401
00:19:38,358 --> 00:19:39,817
--[door clatters]
--[YUZU] We're home!

402
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:42,358
[AKI]
Hm? Welcome back.

403
00:19:42,442 --> 00:19:45,192
Thanks... Hm?

404
00:19:45,275 --> 00:19:47,608
[gasps]
Woah woah, Shiina!

405
00:19:47,692 --> 00:19:50,233
You didn't let Ayaka
drink alcohol, did you?

406
00:19:50,317 --> 00:19:51,692
[AKI]
Uh...

407
00:19:51,775 --> 00:19:54,733
[AYAKA]
Yuzu, welcome back!

408
00:19:54,817 --> 00:19:55,650
[AKI gasps]

409
00:19:55,733 --> 00:19:57,442
[YUZU]
Ms. Ayaka, calm down!

410
00:19:57,525 --> 00:19:58,358
[AYAKA]
Hmm...

411
00:19:58,442 --> 00:19:59,817
[YUZU]
