412
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:02,025
[YUZU groans]

413
00:20:02,108 --> 00:20:04,025
[SUMIRE giggles]

414
00:20:04,108 --> 00:20:06,108
Will someone explain
what's going on?

415
00:20:06,192 --> 00:20:09,442
