421
00:20:23,567 --> 00:20:24,900
I can't let you sacrifice
yourself to that beast!

422
00:20:24,983 --> 00:20:25,858
It's okay.

423
00:20:25,942 --> 00:20:28,025
[SUMIRE, YURI gasp]

424
00:20:28,108 --> 00:20:29,233
[AKI gasps]

425
00:20:31,275 --> 00:20:36,775
[AKI] President. Yamanashi.
