427
00:20:38,442 --> 00:20:42,150
No! I can't just abandon
them and save myself!

428
00:20:42,233 --> 00:20:44,400
I have to do something!

429
00:20:44,483 --> 00:20:47,150
Oh. Look who I found.

430
00:20:47,233 --> 00:20:49,567
[AKI]
And I failed.

431
00:20:49,650 --> 00:20:52,067
[gasps]
