436
00:21:01,525 --> 00:21:04,317
[AKI gasps]
I mean I do, but still!

437
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:06,650
[AKI]
Wait, what am I saying?

438
00:21:06,733 --> 00:21:09,025
[AKI yelps]
Okay pump the breaks!

439
00:21:09,108 --> 00:21:11,108
