443
00:21:28,442 --> 00:21:31,733
I guess I must have fallen
asleep at some point.

444
00:21:31,817 --> 00:21:33,192
Sorry about that.

445
00:21:33,275 --> 00:21:35,733
I like to drink,
but sometimes it can get to me

446
00:21:35,817 --> 00:21:37,400
and I end up falling asleep.

447
00:21:37,483 --> 00:21:40,108
And I tend to forget
what happens during it.

448
00:21:40,192 --> 00:21:41,983
