have a drink together

449
00:21:42,067 --> 00:21:43,650
and you can fill in the gaps.

450
00:21:43,733 --> 00:21:46,275
[AKI chuckles nervously]

451
00:21:46,358 --> 00:21:48,400
[AKI] Well if she doesn't
remember, then I should

452
00:21:48,483 --> 00:21:50,692
