hasn't asked what happened.

453
00:21:50,775 --> 00:21:51,608
[AYAKA]
Akkun?

454
00:21:51,692 --> 00:21:52,775
Yeah?

455
00:21:55,775 --> 00:21:58,233
Don't forget. I'll be waiting.

